odham 100% (2016)\n* [[Nayaki]] (2016)\n* [[Krishna Gaadi Veera Prema Gaadha]] (2016)\n* [[Gentleman (2016 film)|Gentleman]] (2016)\n* [[Andhhagadu]] (2017)\n* [[Supreme (film)|Supreme]] (2016)\n* [[Samanthakamani (film)|Samanthakamani]] (2017)\n* [[Mister (film)|Mister]] (2017)\n* [[Raja The Great]] (2017)\n* [[Jawaan (film)|Jawaan]] (2017)\n* [[Fidaa]] (2017)\n* [[Tholi Prema (2018 film)|Tholi Prema]] (2018)\n* [[Touch Chesi Chudu]] (2018)\n* [[Brand Babu]] (2018)\n* Jamba Lakidi Pamba (2018)\n* [[Vijetha (2018 film)|Vijetha]] (2018)\n* [[Lover (2018 film)|Lover]](2018)\n* [[Srinivasa Kalyanam (2018 film)|Srinivasa Kalyanam]] (2018)\n* [[Nartanasala (2018 film)|Nartansala]] (2018)\n*[[F2 \u2013 Fun and Frustration|F2]] (2019)\n*''[[Viswamitra (film)|Viswamitra]]'' (2019)\n*''[[Prati Roju Pandage]]'' (2019)\n* ''[[Bhagyanagara Veedullo Gamattu]]'' (2019)\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb name|nm1152338}}\n* http://entertainment.oneindia.in/celebs/satyam-rajesh.html\n* http://chithr.com/artist/filmography/495/satyam-rajesh-filmography.html\n* http://vegaentertain.com/vegaentertainment-Six-telugumovie.php\n* http://www.123telugu.com/reviews/K/Kavyas_Dairy/Kavya_Dairy_review.html\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rajesh, Satyam}}\n[[Category:Telugu comedians]]\n[[Category:Telugu male actors]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1979 births]]\n", "text_old": "\n\n{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2015}}\n{{Use Indian English|date=December 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Satyam Rajesh\n| birth_name = Rajesh Babu\n| birth_date={{birth date and age|1974|04|12}}\n| birth_place = [[Visakhapatnam|Visakhapatnam, Andhra Pradesh, India]]\n| residence = [[Hyderabad]], [[Telangana]], [[India]]\n| education = MBA\n| occupation = [[Actor]]\n| mother = Mani Kumari\n| father = Rajendra Prasad\n| Wife = Pallavi\n}}\n'''Satyam Rajesh''' is an Indian actor from Andhra Pradesh who primarily appears in [[Telugu cinema|Telugu films]]. He has acted in more than 350 films <ref name=timesofindia>{{cite web|last1=Palaparthi|first1=Srividya|title=Nayaki will be my first and last movie as a hero: Satyam Rajesh|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/telugu/movies/news/Nayaki-will-be-my-first-and-last-movie-as-a-hero-Satyam-Rajesh/articleshow/51372518.cms|website=timesofindia.indiatimes.com|publisher=Times of India|accessdate=9 November 2016}}</ref> and was nominated a [[Nandi Awards of 2003|Nandi Award]] for Best Comedian for ''[[Satyam (2003 film)|Satyam]]''.\n\n== Early life ==\nRajesh was born in Visakhapatnam as Rajesh Babu. His father is a retired telecom employee and his mother is a homemaker. He studied MBA and worked in Wipro for a pretty long period of time. He got transferred to Hyderabad as a part of his job, which is when he sought opportunities for acting in Telugu films.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reporter|title=\u2018\u0c28\u0c40 \u0c38\u0c4d\u0c28\u0c47\u0c39\u0c02\u2019\u0c24\u0c4b \u0c24\u0c46\u0c30\u0c02\u0c17\u0c47\u0c1f\u0c4d\u0c30\u0c02|url=http://www.sakshi.com/news/andhra-pradesh/chit-chat-with-comedian-rajesh-96078|website=sakshi.com|publisher=\u0c38\u0c3e\u0c15\u0c4d\u0c37\u0c3f|accessdate=9 November 2016}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n\n{{expand list|date=December 2018}}\n{{columns-list|colwidth=22em|\n* [[Jorugaa Husharugaa]] (2002)\n* [[Nee Sneham]] (2002)\n* [[Neeke Manasichchanu]] (2003)\n* [[Satyam (2003 film)|Satyam]] (2003)\n* [[Jai (2004 Telugu film)|Jai]] (2004)\n* [[Gharshana]] (2004)\n* [[Mass (film)|Mass]] (2004)\n*''Keelu Gurram'' (2005)\n* [[Sri (2005 film)|Sri]] (2005)\n* [[Asadhyudu]] (2006)\n* [[Pokiri (2006 film)|Pokiri]] (2006)\n* [[Game (2006 film)|Game]] (2006)\n* [[Desamuduru]] (2007)\n* [[Chandamama (2007 film)|Chandamama]] (2007)\n* [[Chirutha]] (2007)\n* [[Swagatam]] (2008)\n* Bach Ke Zara (2008)\n* [[Krishnarjuna]] (2008)\n* [[Nagaram (2008 film)|Nagaram]] (2008)\n* [[Krishna]] (2008)\n* [[Bommana Brothers Chandana Sisters]] (200