l]]\n===Qualified teams===\nThe top eight teams from Division A, as per the [[2017 Euro Beach Soccer League#League tables|league table]], qualified for the Superfinal.\n{{col-begin|width=60%}}\n{{col-2}}\n*{{beachsoccer|POR}} \n*{{beachsoccer|UKR}} \n*{{beachsoccer|BLR}} \n*{{beachsoccer|ESP}} \n{{col-2}}\n*{{beachsoccer|RUS}}\n*{{beachsoccer|SUI}} \n*{{beachsoccer|ITA}} \n*{{beachsoccer|POL}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n===Group stage===\n''Matches are listed as local time in [[Terracina]], [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]] ([[UTC+2]])''\n\nAll matches took place at the ''Beach Arena \"Carlo Guarnieri\"'', at Spiaggia di Levante<ref name=\"Carlo\"/> with a capacity of around 2,500.<ref name=\"Carlo capacity\"/>\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n====Group 1====\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 97%;\"\n|-\n!width=\"20\"|{{Tooltip|Pos|Position}}\n!width=\"110\"|Team\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|Pld|Played}}\n!width=\"22\"|{{Tooltip|W|Wins}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|W+|Wins after extra time}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|W<small>P</small>|Wins on penalties}}\n!width=\"22\"|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!width=\"25\"|{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|Pts|Points}}\n!width=\"105\"|Notes\n|- style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"\n|1||align=left|{{beachsoccer|POR}}\n|3||3||0||0||0||18||14||+4||'''9'''||Advance to final\n|-\n|2||align=left|{{beachsoccer|ESP}}\n|3||2||0||0||1||18||11||+7||'''6'''||rowspan=\"3\"|\n|-\n|3||align=left|{{beachsoccer|SUI}}\n|3||1||0||0||2||17||21||\u20134||'''3'''\n|-\n|4||align=left|{{beachsoccer|POL}}\n|3||0||0||0||3||15||22||\u20137||'''0'''\n|}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n| date = 14 September 2017\n| time = 13:30\n| team1 = {{beachsoccer-rt|ESP}}\n| score = 7\u20132\n| report = [http://beachsoccerrussia.ru/tournaments/euroleague-2017/matches/4989 Report<small>(ru)</small>]\n| team2 = {{beachsoccer|SUI}}\n| goals1 = Su\u00e1rez {{goal|2||25|