ccer.com/news/ukraine-claim-warnemunde-title |title=Ukraine claim Warnem\u00fcnde title |work=beachsoccer.com |date=27 August 2017 |accessdate=27 August 2017}}</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 97%;\"\n|-\n!colspan=2 width=200|Stage Winners trophy\n!rowspan=2|\n!colspan=3 width=200|Top scorer(s)\n!width=175|Best player\n!width=175|Best goalkeeper\n|- align=center style=\"background: \n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|{{beachsoccer|UKR}}<br><small>(Division A)</small>||{{beachsoccer|ENG}}<br><small>(Division B)</small>||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|ITA}} Michele Di Palma<br>{{flagicon|UKR}} Maksym Voitok||style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flagicon|AZE}} Amid Nazarov<br>{{flagicon|GER}} Sascha Weirauch|| '''3 goals''' || {{flagicon|UKR}} Roman Pachev || {{flagicon|GER}} Toni Muller\n|}\n\n==League tables==\n<!-- Don't update until a stage is complete -->\n''At stage completion''\n\n<small>'''Ranking & tie-breaking criteria:''' Division A \u2013 1. Points earned 2. Goal difference 3. Goals scored | Division B \u2013 1. Highest group placement 2. Points earned 3. Goal difference 4. Goals scored 5. Results against 4th place team</small>\n{{col-begin}}{{col-2}}\n\n=== Division A ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 95%;\"\n!width=\"20\" height=\"41\"|{{Tooltip|Pos|Position}}\n!width=\"120\"|Team\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|Pld|Played}}\n!width=\"22\"|{{Tooltip|W|Wins}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|W+|Wins after extra time}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|W<small>P</small>|Wins on penalties}}\n!width=\"22\"|{{Tooltip|L|Lost}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|GF|Goals for}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|GA|Goals against}}\n!width=\"25\"|{{Tooltip|GD|Goal difference}}\n!width=\"18\"|{{Tooltip|Pts|Points}}\n!width=\"105\"|Notes\n|- style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"\n|1||align=left|{{beachsoccer|POR}} \n|6||4||1||1||0||40||23||+17||'''15'''||rowspan=\"8\"|Advance to<br>Superfinal\n|- style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"\n|2||align=lef